Package: CaliCo
Type: Package
Title: Code calibration in a Bayesian framework
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Mathieu Carmassi <mathieu.carmassi@gmail.fr> [aut, cre]"))
Maintainer: Mathieu Carmassi <mathieu.carmassi@gmail.com>
Description: Calibration of every computational code. It uses a Bayesian framework to rule the estimation. With a new data set, the prediction will create a prevision set taking into account the new calibrated parameters. The choices between several models is also available.
